        <h1>Travel to Costa Rica! 
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Flag_of_Costa_Rica_%28state%29.svg/640px-Flag_of_Costa_Rica_%28state%29.svg.png" width="40">
        </h1> 
        <h2>A tropical destination in Central America.</h2>

        <h3 id="natural-rainforests"> Boundless natural rainforests</h3>

        <p>Costa Rica takes up 1.5% of the total land space on Earth but accounts for <strong>3% of its biodiversity</strong>.</p>
        <p>What does this mean for one visiting the country? This means that you're going to have access to some of the most incredible protected lands in the world.</p>

        <h3 id="english-speaking">High English-speaking population</h3>

        <p>For over half a century the country dismantled its armed forces in order to better invest this money into its education. Its incredible public schooling ensures that most of the population can <em>communicate</em> and <em>articulate</em> in the language. This knowledge of the universal language ensures that you won't ever feel uncomfortable in your stay.</p>

        <h3 id="flora-fauna">Stunning flora and fauna</h3>

        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/HeliconiusDorisLinnaeus.jpg/300px-HeliconiusDorisLinnaeus.jpg">

        <p>Captivating fauna that you won't be able to find anywhere else</p>

        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/61/Camino_de_Costa_Rica_Ave_Sol_River_Sanctuary_Volc%C3%A1n_Turrialba_River_Pacuare.jpg/2560px-Camino_de_Costa_Rica_Ave_Sol_River_Sanctuary_Volc%C3%A1n_Turrialba_River_Pacuare.jpg" width="300">

        <p>And breathtaking flora that you wish to live in.</p>

